text: Fahad Jaber Al-Marri (born 1986) is a Qatari professional football referee.Profile He has been a full international for FIFA from 2012 to 2018.FIFA. "Qatar: Referees". He refereed some matches in AFC Champions League. == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Qatari football referees
